Package: magnum-plugins
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, magnum, libdevil1c2, libjpeg8, libpng16-16, libfaad2, libfreetype6, libassimp3v5|libassimp4
Description: Plugins for the Magnum C++11/C++14 graphics engine
 Magnum is 2D/3D graphics engine written in C++11 and modern OpenGL. Its goal
 is to simplify low-level graphics development and interaction with OpenGL
 using recent C++11 features and to abstract away platform-specific issues.
